'''2016年拉合尔炸弹袭击'''是指2016年3月27日发生在[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[旁遮普省|旁遮普省]]首府[[拉合尔|拉合尔]]的自杀式炸弹袭击。袭击发生在当地公园的[[复活节|复活节]]活动中，共造成至少70人死亡，300多人受伤。[[塔利班|塔利班]]组织分支{{le|自由人党|Jamaat-ul-Ahrar}}已宣称对袭击事件负责，并称其目标是巴基斯坦的基督教徒。<ref name="CNN">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/27/asia/pakistan-lahore-deadly-blast/|title=In Pakistan, Taliban's Easter bombing targets, kills scores of Christians|work=CNN|date=2016-03-27|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402032223/http://www.cnn.com/2016/03/27/asia/pakistan-lahore-deadly-blast/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-pakistan-blast-idUSKCN0WT0HR|title=Pakistanis hunt militants behind blast that killed at least 70|work=Reuters|date=2016-03-28|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327225220/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-pakistan-blast-idUSKCN0WT0HR|dead-url=no}}</ref>死者中包括基督教徒和穆斯林，至少包含29名儿童。<ref name="WashPost">{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/death-toll-in-pakistan-easter-suicide-attack-rises-to-72-authorities-vow-to-hunt-down-perpetrators/2016/03/28/037a2e18-f46a-11e5-958d-d038dac6e718_story.html|title=Death toll in Pakistan bombing climbs past 70|work=Washington Post|date=2016-03-28|accessdate=2016-03-31|archive-date=2016-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331201838/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/death-toll-in-pakistan-easter-suicide-attack-rises-to-72-authorities-vow-to-hunt-down-perpetrators/2016/03/28/037a2e18-f46a-11e5-958d-d038dac6e718_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
巴基斯坦长期遭受暴力袭击和冲突，自2003年起已有超过21,000名平民在各类军事冲突中丧生。[[巴基斯坦塔利班|巴基斯坦塔利班]]及其分支组织在近年内频繁活动，在该国北部多次制造袭击事件，企图推翻现政府。<ref name="latimes"/>巴基斯坦人口以[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]为主，基督教徒在巴基斯坦总人口中约占1.6%，是该国仅次于[[印度教|印度教徒]]的第二大少数族裔，经常成为极端组织的袭击目标，且类似袭击有逐年增加的趋势。<ref name="BBC claim"/>

[[拉合尔|拉合尔]]是巴基斯坦的第二大城市，也是[[巴基斯坦总理|该国总理]][[纳瓦兹·谢里夫|纳瓦兹·谢里夫]]的权力基础之所在。这座城市在此前也遭受过类似的袭击：2015年，拉合尔两座基督教堂遇袭；2014年，拉合尔附近的印巴边境村落[[瓦加|瓦加]]也遭受了袭击。<ref name="WashPost"/>

== 经过 ==
当地时间2016年3月27日下午6:30左右，在[[旁遮普省|旁遮普省]]首府[[拉合尔|拉合尔]]的{{lang|en|Gulshan-e-Iqbal}}公园发生爆炸。<ref name="nation">{{cite news|url=http://nation.com.pk/national/27-Mar-2016/at-least-15-injured-in-gulshan-iqbal-blast-in-lahore|title=70 dead, 340 injured in Gulshan-e-Iqbal suicide blast in Lahore|work=The Nation|date=2016-03-27|accessdate=2016-03-27|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224181519/https://nation.com.pk/27-Mar-2016/at-least-15-injured-in-gulshan-iqbal-blast-in-lahore|dead-url=no}}</ref>事发时，公园正在进行[[复活节|复活节]]活动，不少家庭正在公园出游。袭击者在公园主入口停车区附近引爆身上的炸弹，炸弹中装有[[滚珠轴承|钢珠]]。<ref name="aljazeera"/><ref name="BBC claim"/>爆炸地点距离儿童秋千区不远，因此死者中有大量的妇女儿童。爆炸造成严重破坏，有目击者称见到“火焰高过树木，尸体飞向空中”。爆炸发生后还引发了人群踩踏，共造成至少70人死亡，300多人受伤，死者中包括至少29名儿童。<ref name="BBC attack">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35908512|work=BBC|title=Pakistan explosion leaves many dead at Lahore park|date=2016-03-28|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201074530/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35908512|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN"/><ref name="reuters"/><ref name="aljazeera">{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/03/deadly-blast-hits-pakistan-lahore-160327143110195.html|title=Scores killed in attack on park in Pakistan's Lahore|work=Aljazeera|date=2016-03-28|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327221816/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/03/deadly-blast-hits-pakistan-lahore-160327143110195.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WashPost"/>爆炸发生后，当地急救系统随即爆满，救护车数量不足，不少伤者只能乘坐出租车或电动三轮车自行赶往医院。<ref name="latimes">{{cite news|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/la-fg-pakistan-blast-20160327-story.html|title=Taliban says it targeted Christians in a park on Easter Sunday, killing 65|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2016-03-27|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2018-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224181516/https://www.latimes.com/world/la-fg-pakistan-blast-20160327-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

爆炸后，警方认定为自杀性袭击。[[塔利班|塔利班]]组织分支{{le|自由人党|Jamaat-ul-Ahrar}}宣称对袭击事件负责，并宣称其目标是巴基斯坦的[[基督教徒|基督教徒]]，同时称将继续进行此类袭击。<ref name="CNN"/><ref name="BBC claim">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35909677|title=Pakistan Taliban faction claims park attack on Lahore Christians|work=BBC|date=2016-03-28|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328040442/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35909677|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 反应 ==
爆炸发生后，[[巴基斯坦总统|巴基斯坦总统]][[馬姆努恩·侯賽因|馬姆努恩·侯賽因]]和总理[[纳瓦兹·谢里夫|纳瓦兹·谢里夫]]谴责了袭击，对逝者表示了哀悼。旁遮普省首席部长{{le|夏巴兹·谢里夫|Shehbaz Sharif}}尤其谴责了针对儿童的暴力，称袭击者“不配为人”。当地政府也宣布将悼念三天。[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]表示袭击“骇人听闻”。<ref name="BBC claim"/>[[印度|印度]]、[[美国|美国]]、[[英国|英国]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]等国政府和领导人也对袭击事件表示谴责。<ref name="CNN"/><ref name="telegraph">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/pakistan/12205457/Pakistan-terror-attack-69-dead-after-suicide-bomber-strikes-childrens-play-area-in-Lahore.html|title=Pakistan terror attack: 69 dead after suicide bomber strikes children's play area in Lahore|work=Telegraph|date=2016-03-27|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328135908/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/pakistan/12205457/Pakistan-terror-attack-69-dead-after-suicide-bomber-strikes-childrens-play-area-in-Lahore.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

